reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 9, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Was so excited about this product, once I got them I was ticked off. Not only are they stickers but the glossy finish makes them look horrible. Waste of money.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 21, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Love more than I thought I would!
reviews.reviewText: I thought it was baskets when I first ordered. I wasn’t paying attention and actually reading. But when I saw the reviews, it hadn’t been delivered but was on the way. I just knew I was about to pack it back up and send it back. However, it got here and I gave it a chance. I placed them the way the picture was advertised. My walls are a light blue-ish color and idk how but these little stickers didn’t disappoint with the colors. KEY TO GETTING THEM TO STICK AND NOT BUBBLE….CLEAN THE WALL! It looks great! No bubbling. Only been up for 15 min but looks great!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 1, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars So tacky and cheap looking
reviews.reviewText: When these arrived I was so disappointed. The description seemed as if they were adhesive baskets not actual flat stickers. They are not even 3D printed, they’re shiny/glossy and stick out like a sore thumb in my boho bedroom. I thought if I put them up maybe I’d like them but I absolutely hate them. Definitely don’t waste your money on this product!!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 7, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I wish this product would stick better to the walls. I have used decals before on my daughter’s bedroom. These are not as good. They crease and bubble even after running a tool over them. I do not have a textured wall. So I am not sure what is causing the issue.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 8, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This is probably the worst purchase I’ve ever made. Not only are they stickers but they are super small, cheesy and don’t last long - not flat at least. Not too sticky either.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 28, 2022
reviews.reviewText: They are NOT what is pictured at all. These are my top 3 bones to pick with this product, and yes there are more… but these are what irked me the most.1) if you have any type of humidity in your home, or where ever you decide to stick these, they WILL start to peel off the wall. I’ve had these a few days, and by the evening of when I stuck them up the day I got them they were already coming off, even though I followed the instructions. And they won’t stop peeling… no matter what I do…2) they have this awful pinkish tint to the “background” and boarder on them, so if you have any other color wall that’s different than the background and boarder on them, even the most basic white paint color, you WILL see the left over boarder AND background on these, which really bugs me… a lot. It looks like a dirty ring behind and around the baskets.3) they are SUPER glossy!!!! So they of course do not even for a second pass off as real baskets… they would have been a lot more realistic in a matte vinyl.
